    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show signs of its age and mileage. The engine starts and runs, but you may notice some minor fluid leaks and a rougher idle than a newer model. The exterior has several visible scratches and a few small dents, while the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and some fading on the dashboard plastics. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a lower price point, provided they are willing to address some minor mechanical and cosmetic upkeep in the near future.",
